parameters.query:
SELECT 
  rm.render_id,
  rm.channel_id,
  rm.video_type,
  rm.performance_params,
  rm.scenes,
  ya.video_id,
  ya.views,
  ya.ctr,
  ya.avg_view_duration,
  ya.retention_rate,
  ya.likes,
  ya.comments,
  (ya.likes + ya.comments * 2) / NULLIF(ya.views, 0) as engagement_score
FROM render_metadata rm
JOIN youtube_analytics ya ON rm.youtube_video_id = ya.video_id
WHERE 
  ya.recorded_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '{{ $json.analysis_window_days }} days'
  AND ya.views >= {{ $json.min_views }}
ORDER BY ya.retention_rate DESC
LIMIT 100

INSERT INTO evolution_params_history (
  optimized_params,
  analysis_summary,
  applied_at
) VALUES (
  $1::jsonb,
  $2::jsonb,
  NOW()
) RETURNING id

UPDATE system_config 
SET value = $1::jsonb, updated_at = NOW()
WHERE key = 'default_performance_params'

INSERT INTO regenerate_queue (
  render_id,
  new_params,
  priority,
  reason,
  status,
  queued_at
) VALUES (
  $1,
  $2::jsonb,
  $3,
  $4,
  'pending',
  NOW()
)
